high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the egg in the top compartment of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter, then face the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg in a microwave.

high_descs: Make a left to face the countertop.
Pick up the egg from the countertop.
Make a left to walk towards the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge, removing it again.
Make a left to walk to the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg in the fridge to put it in the microwave.

high_descs: turn left and move to the table
Pick up a potato from the table
turn left and head to the fridge
place the potato to cool in the fridge and take it out
turn right and head to the microwave oven
place the potato in the microwave oven
anns.task_desc: place a cold potato in the oven
